trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls used to track and manage related groups of controls.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller som brukes til å spore og administrere relaterte grupper med kontroller.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartCollection class is a read-only collection of controls, typically used by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> controls to manage sets of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartCollection er en skrivebeskyttet samling kontroller, som vanligvis brukes av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>Kontroller for å administrere tegnsett <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses a WebPartCollection object to keep a list of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls on a page, whereas a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> control uses a WebPartCollection object to track the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls that it contains.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll bruker et WebPartCollection-objekt til å gjøre en liste over alle den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollerer på en side, mens en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>kontroll bruker et WebPartCollection-objekt for sporing av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollene som den inneholder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The WebPartCollection collection contains both <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls and other server controls (such as user controls, custom controls, and ASP.NET controls) that are placed in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zones and used as part of Web Parts applications.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For WebPartCollection samlingen inneholder både <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller og andre serverkontroller (for eksempel brukerkontroller egendefinerte kontroller og ASP.NET-kontroller) plasseres i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>Sikkerhetssoner og brukes som en del av webdeler programmer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: So, for example, if you have a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> zone in a page, and within it you declare a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control and the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar> control, both controls will be in the WebPartCollection collection referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Dette er tilfellet, for eksempel hvis du har en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>sone på en side, og i den deklarere en egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll og ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar>kontroll, blir begge kontrollene i samlingen WebPartCollection refererer til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartCollection object exists so that the Web Parts control set can work with strongly typed collections.
trans-unit.target: WebPartCollection-objektet finnes slik at webdeler kontrollen settet kan arbeide med forespørselsparameter av sterk type samlinger.

trans-unit.source: Similarly, if you want to perform mass operations on a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, you can get a reference to a WebPartCollection object using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: På samme måte hvis du vil utføre for operasjoner i et sett med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller, kan du hente en referanse til en WebPartCollection objektet ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: For example, you might want to loop through all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls on a page and change their appearance in some way.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel gå gjennom alle de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>på en side og endre utseendet på en måte.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Even though the WebPartCollection object is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the properties of the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Selv om WebPartCollection-objektet er skrivebeskyttet, kan du endre programmatisk egenskapene for de underliggende kontrollene det refereres til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en tom ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartCollection constructor initializes an empty instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren WebPartCollection initialiserer en tom forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: The object itself is read-only and has no method to add individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls to it; therefore, you will have little occasion to use this constructor.
trans-unit.target: Selve objektet er skrivebeskyttet og har ingen metode for å legge til individuelle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller den; derfor må du få bruk for å benytte denne konstruktøren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"></xref> object by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"> </xref> objektet ved å sende i en <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartCollection constructor initializes an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> class by passing in a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren WebPartCollection initialiserer en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>klasse ved å sende i en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: Although a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object is read-only and there is no method for adding individual controls to it, you can create your own <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of controls, and pass that to the WebPartCollection constructor.
trans-unit.target: Selv om en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objektet er skrivebeskyttet, og det finnes ingen metode for å legge til individuelle kontroller, kan du opprette dine egne <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>samling av kontroller, og som sendes til konstruktøren WebPartCollection.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: This enables you to create custom collections and perform bulk operations on them.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør at du kan opprette tilpassede samlinger og utføre masseoperasjoner på dem..

trans-unit.source: You can also access the underlying controls in the collection and change their property values programmatically.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også tilgang til underliggende kontrollene i samlingen og endre egenskapsverdiene programmatisk.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: webParts is .
trans-unit.target: webPartsis .

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular control exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om en bestemt kontroll finnes i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Contains method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> object and determine whether it is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Contains lar deg kontrollere en bestemt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>objekt og finne ut om det er en del av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> som er merket av for å finne ut om den er i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular control is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En boolsk verdi som angir om en bestemt kontroll i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Kopierer samlingen til en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object, a subset of those controls, or a superset of those controls.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CopyTo er nyttig når du ønsker å sette sammen en egendefinert matrise kan inneholde den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objekt, et delsett av kontrollene og overordnet kontrollene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> objects to contain the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> objekter kan inneholde kopierte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: Startpunktet i matrisen som skal plasseres samlingen innholdet.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer posisjonen for en bestemt medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method is useful if you have multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls on a Web Parts page, and you need to know the ordinal position of one control relative to the others.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IndexOf er nyttig hvis du har flere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller i en webdeler, og du må vite ordenstall plasseringen av en kontroll i forhold til de andre.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> that is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> som et medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir posisjonen til et bestemt objekt i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a member of the collection based on its position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et medlem i samlingen basert på plasseringen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Item indexer allows you to access the underlying <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object by index, and change their property values or call methods.
trans-unit.target: Indeksering for elementet får du tilgang til den underliggende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objekt av indeksen, og endre egenskapsverdiene eller kalle metoder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The index of a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control in a collection.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for en bestemt <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen i en samling.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> i den angitte indeksen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a member of the collection based on a unique string identifier.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et medlem i samlingen basert på en unik streng-identifikator.

trans-unit.source: The Item indexer enables you to access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object according to a unique identifier.
trans-unit.target: Elementet indeksering får du tilgang til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollere i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objektet i henhold til en unik identifikator.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The Web Parts control set performs case-insensitive matching on this property, so case sensitivity is not part of a unique `id` value.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For webdeler kontrollsett utfører samlingstype samsvar for denne egenskapen, så store og små bokstaver ikke er en del av en unik `id` verdi.

trans-unit.source: The Item property also works to identify members of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object in some specialized cases.
trans-unit.target: Elementegenskapen fungerer også for å identifisere medlemmene i et <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objektet i enkelte tilfeller spesialiserte.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: In the case of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> controls, the indexer is able to match the identifier for the underlying child control wrapped by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>kontroller, indeksering får til å samsvare med identifikatoren for den underliggende underordnede kontrollen står av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>

trans-unit.source: In the case of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart> controls, the indexer matches the identifier for the control based on a case-insensitive comparison of the `id` parameter and either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.OriginalID%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.GenericWebPartID%2A> property values.
trans-unit.target: Med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart>kontroller, indeksering samsvarer med identifikatoren for kontroll basert på en samlingstype sammenligning av den `id` parameteren og enten den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.OriginalID%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.GenericWebPartID%2A>egenskapsverdier.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.GenericWebPartID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.OriginalID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart>

trans-unit.source: The unique identifier for a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control in a collection.
trans-unit.target: Den unike identifikatoren for en bestemt <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen i en samling.

trans-unit.source: The first in the collection whose ID equals the value of id.
trans-unit.target: Først med IDen er lik verdien i samlingen id .
